/linux/blob/master/fs/binfmt_elf.c) in the kernel ignores the `p_align` field of the ELF program headers and assumes page-alignment instead.", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/70022/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/70022/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}